<item>
            <title>[LU-7693] umount hang on MDS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7693</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Error happen during soak testing of build &apos;20160119&apos; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/Releases/Soak+Testing+on+Lola#SoakTestingonLola-20160119&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/Releases/Soak+Testing+on+Lola#SoakTestingonLola-20160119&lt;/a&gt;). build is based on master branch. DNE is enabled. MDTs had been formatted using &lt;em&gt;ldiskfs&lt;/em&gt;, OSTs using &lt;em&gt;zfs&lt;/em&gt; as backend.&lt;br/&gt;
Environment description: &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/Releases/Soak+Testing+on+Lola#SoakTestingonLola-Configuration&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/Releases/Soak+Testing+on+Lola#SoakTestingonLola-Configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The incident occurred during a normal &apos;umount&apos; - process of the Lustre FS.&lt;br/&gt;
Sequence of events:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Clients successful unmounted&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;All server node successful unmounted besides MDTs (mdt-6,7) on &lt;tt&gt;lola-11&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;umount&lt;/tt&gt; is stalled on &lt;tt&gt;lola-11&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Forced stack trace of processe on &lt;tt&gt;lola-11&lt;/tt&gt;, created kernel debug log, and attached messages, console, and debug log to ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
